gov.va.vinci.leo.ae

Class LeoBaseAnnotator.Param

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.vinci.leo.ae.LeoBaseAnnotator.Param
  • Enclosing class:
    LeoBaseAnnotator

    public static class LeoBaseAnnotator.Param
extends Object
    A set of default parameters for the base annotation. Extending annotators may use persist parameters from a parent class by extending the inner Param from the parent as in: public static class Param extends LeoBaseAnnotator.param {} Each field represents an annotation parameter and utilizes the UIMA ConfigurationParameter as in the declaration:

    public static ConfigurationParameter PARAMETER_NAME = new ConfigurationParameterImpl("name", "description", "type", isMandatory, isMultivalued, new String[]{});
